WEBVTT

00:14:59.276 --> 00:15:00.427
That's it.

00:15:00.451 --> 00:15:04.713
(Applause)

00:15:04.737 --> 00:15:06.832
I have solved it all, right?

00:15:06.856 --> 00:15:08.007
That's it.

00:15:08.031 --> 00:15:09.190
That is pretty much --

00:15:09.214 --> 00:15:10.381
there's a few details --

00:15:10.405 --> 00:15:12.359
but that's pretty much all we have to do.

00:15:12.383 --> 00:15:14.106
It's not that complicated, right?

00:15:15.556 --> 00:15:16.843
But it's hard.

00:15:18.279 --> 00:15:22.739
The hate that we feel
towards certain groups of people

00:15:23.814 --> 00:15:26.662
because of who they are
or what they believe

00:15:26.686 --> 00:15:30.098
is so ingrained in our minds
and in our society